{assign var="active" value="marketingm"}

<div class="row login">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <div class="shopyheader">
                <h2>{l s='Marketing modules included' mod='shopylinkerp'}</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-10 shopyinfopanel">
                <div class="" id="modalimg"></div>
                <h2>{l s='Marketing modules included' mod='shopylinkerp'}</h2>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question1" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="question1">
                        {l s='Cross Selling' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse in" id="question1">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="With this tool, you will be able to offer visitors products or services that might interest them or that you want to highlight, thus avoiding them having to waste time searching your PrestaShop catalogue. You will be able to perform different types of cross-sells simultaneously to increase the average cart value and improve the user experience." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/cross-sales/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yj3AzQY3J8w"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Introduction Cross Selling' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>
                            <a data-image-url="Selector%20de%20la%20configuraci%C3%B3n%20del%20tipo%20de%20Venta%20Cruzada.png" data-target="#modalimg" class="linkinfo imagelink" href="#"
                              >{l s='Cross-Sell type configuration selector' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Ver_imagen"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question2" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question2">
                        {l s='Quick Sales' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse " id="question2">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="This functionality gives the user the ability to make purchases without having to visit the product page. By including a fully customizable button on the listing pages, which also allows you to select combinations and quantities, simplifying the purchase process. Ideal for repeat purchases." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/quick-sales/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=knr2F8iixSo"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Introduction Quick Sales' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question3" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question3">
                        {l s='Merchandising in Front Listings' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question3">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="It is a complete system for organizing and prioritizing products, categories and brands on store listings and search results pages. It offers 15 ordering criteria and in ascending and descending order, allowing to prioritize the first positions and place the products without stock at the end. This gives you the most appropriate way to present your PrestaShop listings, increasing the visibility of the products you are most interested in selling." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/store-front-listings-merchandising/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BvVzZLlKExM"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Introduction Merchandising in front listings' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question4" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question4">
                        {l s='Rating system' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question4">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="This system allows your customers to register ratings and comments about your products and the store. In this way, your visitors can feel safe knowing the experience of other buyers before making a purchase decision. In addition, it has configuration options to adapt the type of registration, design and moderation by the store." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/rating-system/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RRrglr03Tf8"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Introduction Rating System' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question5" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question5">
                        {l s='WhatsApp' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question5">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="With this tool, you will be able to add personalized buttons to your store, adapted to each type of page, so that visitors can communicate with you or with the different departments of your company through WhatsApp with just one click. In addition, you can assign multiple users to attend the same WhatsApp line. This will allow you to improve communication with your customers, resolve questions and problems, and provide them with quality service." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/whatsapp/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j1aCvqJddJw"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Introduction WhatsApp' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question6" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question6">
                        {l s='Advanced search engine' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question6">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="Using this search engine, visitors can enter as few as 3 characters in the search field and they will instantly see matching results (including images) in a popup window. As more characters are entered, the results will update automatically. In addition, it gives them the possibility to filter the results according to the properties of the products, applying filters of categories, brands, attribute values and characteristics." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s="Administrators will not have to worry about updating the browser's cache as they do with other browsers, since the queries to the server are made in real time." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/advanced-search-engine/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wxj4qvCeebI"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Introduction Predictive Search Engine' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question7" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question7">
                        {l s='Rich Texts' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question7">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="This feature automatically adds microcodes to your HTML code to make your content easier for search engines to understand, which has a significant impact on organic ranking. It is applied on the product pages, in category and/or brand listings, and in the evaluations of each product or of the store in general." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/funciones/textos-enriquecidos/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question8" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question8">
                        {l s='Faceted Navigation System' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question8">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="It's a comprehensive system that allows your visitors to filter products based on their properties in both store listings and searches, making it very easy to quickly find the products they're interested in. In addition, you will be able to configure personalized navigation schemes for each of the categories of the store." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/facets-navigation-system/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEIb8fcBU5w"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Introduction Faceted Navigation System' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question9" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question9">
                        {l s='Bid Timer' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question9">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="With this functionality, you will be able to add a timer on the product page, which will show the time left to take advantage of a special offer. In this way, you will generate a feeling of urgency in store visitors, encouraging them to make their purchase without delay." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/offer-timer/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question10" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question10">
                        {l s='Loyalty and Coupons System' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question10">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="This system rewards customers with points for their purchases and allows them to redeem them for discount coupons. In addition, you can configure the generation of post-sale coupons, this means that discount coupons will be automatically generated for those customers who make purchases that meet certain conditions established by the store." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/loyalty-system-and-coupons/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QYKHHSfvfGE"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Loyalty and Coupons System' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question11" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question11">
                        {l s='Advanced Product Comparison' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question11">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="This functionality allows you to take advantage of the extensive information in the catalog to offer shoppers the most relevant comparisons between similar products. Within a single configurable product comparison page, they can easily and quickly find all the information they need to make an informed decision. In addition, you will be able to assign characteristics to the categories so that the system verifies the consistency between the similar products and thus guarantees that the comparisons made by the users are really effective. You can even enable the ability for users to compare products from different categories, depending on the settings you set." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/product-comparison/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VpchePhrfO0"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Introduction Advanced Comparison' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
            {include file="module:shopylinkerp/views/templates/admin/sidebar.tpl" var=active}
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
